# Local dev: leave unset to use ./data/ (filesystem).
#
# Vercel production: create a Blob store (Project → Storage → Blob) and connect
# it to this project. Vercel injects BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN automatically.
# Without it, uploads fail with EROFS (read-only filesystem on /var/task).
#
# BLOB_READ_WRITE_TOKEN=
